<body>
    <h1>High-Level Design/Implementation plan for: Layered MVP Implementati=
on for Codebase Intelligence</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplemen=
tationforCodebaseIntelligence-High-LevelDesign+ImplementationPlan">High-Lev=
el Design + Implementation Plan</h1>
<p>For: Layered MVP Implementation for Codebase Intelligence</p>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-1.Goal">1. Goal</h2>
<p>This document proposes a concrete way to add the Codebase Intelligence M=
VP into the <strong>current</strong> <code>bitloops_cli</code> codebase, wi=
th:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>An explicit overall folder structure</p></li>
<li>
<p>Folder/file-level responsibilities</p></li>
<li>
<p>A step-by-step implementation plan</p></li>
<li>
<p>Early refactorings that should happen first to reduce risk</p></li>
</ol>
<p>It is intentionally designed for an <strong>evolutionary migration</stro=
ng> (not a big-bang rewrite), because the repository already has working CL=
I/hook/dashboard/devql behavior.</p>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-2.DesignDecisionSummary">2. Design Decision Summary</=
h2>
<p>Adopt a <strong>hybrid architecture</strong>:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Capability-first at the application layer</strong> (<code>blast_=
radius</code>, <code>historical_intent</code>, <code>test_harness</code>, <=
code>semantic_clones</code>, <code>runtime_provenance</code>)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Layered internals beneath it</strong> (static analysis, behaviou=
ral, provenance, semantic, runtime)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Explicit ports/adapters</strong> for git/storage/external system=
s</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Separated read vs write paths</strong> (query path latency isola=
tion from ingestion throughput)</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this is preferred:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better cohesion than a pure layer-only tree (features are owned end-to-e=
nd)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Lower coupling than today (commands/hook runtime stop owning domain logi=
c)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Better testability (use cases can be tested against ports with fakes)</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>Lower migration risk (old command surfaces can wrap new services increme=
ntally)</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-3.TargetFolderStructure">3. Target Folder Structure</=
h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: text; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s_cli/src/
  intelligence/
    mod.rs
    composition_root.rs

    contracts/
      mod.rs
      ids.rs
      snapshots.rs
      artefacts.rs
      graph.rs
      history.rs
      tests.rs
      clones.rs
      provenance.rs
      errors.rs
      policies.rs

    application/
      mod.rs
      capabilities/
        blast_radius.rs
        historical_intent.rs
        test_harness.rs
        semantic_clones.rs
        runtime_provenance.rs
      planner/
        context_bundle_planner.rs
        budget_policy.rs
      services/
        snapshot_resolver.rs
        candidate_ranker.rs

    ingestion/
      mod.rs
      orchestrator.rs
      bootstrap_backfill.rs
      incremental_git.rs
      workspace_overlay.rs
      checkpoints_bridge.rs
      telemetry_bridge.rs

    static_analysis/
      mod.rs
      parser.rs
      graph_builder.rs
      extractors/
        mod.rs
        rust.rs
        typescript.rs
        javascript.rs

    behavioural/
      mod.rs
      test_linker.rs
      coverage_mapper.rs
      recommendation.rs

    provenance/
      mod.rs
      intent_linker.rs
      timeline_builder.rs
      external_refs.rs

    semantic/
      mod.rs
      embedding_pipeline.rs
      clone_index.rs
      similarity_search.rs

    query/
      mod.rs
      devql/
        mod.rs
        planner.rs
        stages/
          as_of.rs
          artefacts.rs
          blast_radius.rs
          tests.rs
          intent.rs
          clones.rs
          provenance.rs

    adapters/
      mod.rs
      git/
        client.rs
      storage/
        relational.rs
        events.rs
        vector.rs
      external/
        jira.rs
        confluence.rs
        pr_metadata.rs
      llm/
        enrich.rs

    observability/
      mod.rs
      metrics.rs
      tracing.rs</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-4.ResponsibilityMap(Folder+FileLevel)">4. Responsibil=
ity Map (Folder + File Level)</h2>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-4.1RootIntelligenceModule">4.1 Root Intelligence Modu=
le</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Path</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Responsibility</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Why this placement</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>intelligence/mod.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Public module surface and exports</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Single entry point for commands/hooks/dashboard integration</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>intelligence/composition_root.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Wires implementations to ports for runtime boot</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Keeps dependency wiring out of business logic</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-4.2ContractsLayer(StableDomainInterfaces)">4.2 Contra=
cts Layer (Stable Domain Interfaces)</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Path</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Responsibility</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Why this placement</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/ids.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Canonical identifiers (repo, commit, snapshot, artefact, symbol)</p></td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Avoids id-shape drift across modules</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/snapshots.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Snapshot model + precedence rules DTOs</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Centralizes temporal semantics</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/artefacts.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Artefact and symbol contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Shared language across static/query/ingest</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/graph.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Edge and blast-radius contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Stable API for dependency graph use cases</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/history.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Historical intent/rationale contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Encodes provenance payload shape</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/tests.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Test/coverage linkage contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Shared between behavioural + query</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/clones.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Embedding and clone result contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Decouples semantic layer internals</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/provenance.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Runtime provenance and telemetry join contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Cross-layer runtime context abstraction</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/errors.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Domain error categories</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Consistent error handling and observability</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>contracts/policies.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ranking and budget policy contracts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Explicit, testable policy boundaries</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-4.3ApplicationLayer(UseCases)">4.3 Application Layer =
(Use Cases)</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Path</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Responsibility</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Why this placement</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/capabilities/blast_radius.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Main use case: impact analysis from symbol/file/commit</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>High-value capability with strong invariants</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/capabilities/historical_intent.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Main use case: intent timeline and rationale retrieval</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Keeps history logic cohesive</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/capabilities/test_harness.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Main use case: test recommendation and coverage mapping</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Encapsulates behavioural retrieval policy</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/capabilities/semantic_clones.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Main use case: nearest semantic siblings and divergence</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Isolates vector strategy from query syntax</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/capabilities/runtime_provenance.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Main use case: runtime signal to code/provenance joins</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Encapsulates operational context logic</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/planner/context_bundle_planner.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Candidate selection and ranking orchestration</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Keeps =E2=80=9CPod C-like=E2=80=9D ranking out of adapters</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/planner/budget_policy.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Token-budget and diversity policy</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Explicit optimization policy component</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/services/snapshot_resolver.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Resolve workspace/ref/commit precedence</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Shared by query and hook prefetch paths</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>application/services/candidate_ranker.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Deterministic ranking/scoring logic</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Allows offline benchmarking and regression tests</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-4.4IngestionLayer(WritePath)">4.4 Ingestion Layer (Wr=
ite Path)</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Path</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Responsibility</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Why this placement</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>ingestion/orchestrator.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Coordinates all ingestion lanes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Single workflow coordinator</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>ingestion/bootstrap_backfill.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>One-time baseline ingestion</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Separate from continuous operations</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>ingestion/incremental_git.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Commit/ref-driven incremental updates</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Isolates high-frequency update logic</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>ingestion/workspace_overlay.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Uncommitted workspace snapshot ingestion</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Explicitly models developer-local state</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>ingestion/checkpoints_bridge.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pulls checkpoint metadata/transcripts into intelligence model</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Reuses existing Bitloops value without duplication</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>ingestion/telemetry_bridge.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Curates event stream into provenance-ready tables</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Decouples raw telemetry from query model</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-4.5StaticAnalysisLayer">4.5 Static Analysis Layer</h3=
>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Path</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Responsibility</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Why this placement</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>static_analysis/parser.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Tree-sitter parse pipeline + tolerant parsing</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Shared parser entry point</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>static_analysis/graph_builder.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Builds symbol/import/call/type edges</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Central graph construction boundary</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>static_analysis/extractors/rust.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rust artefact extraction</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Language-specific strategy isolation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>static_analysis/extractors/typescript.rs</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>TypeScript artefact extraction</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Language-specific strategy isolation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>static_analysis/extractors/javascript.rs</code></p></td>
