<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-5.DependencyRules(ArchitectureGuardrails)">5. Depende=
ncy Rules (Architecture Guardrails)</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><code>contracts/*</code> must not depend on any adapter or command modul=
e.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>application/*</code> can depend only on <code>contracts/*</code> a=
nd pure utility modules.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>ingestion/*</code> and <code>query/*</code> call <code>application=
/*</code>; they do not call each other directly.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>adapters/*</code> implement contracts/ports and contain infra-spec=
ific code only.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>commands/*</code>, <code>engine/hooks/*</code>, and <code>server/*=
</code> use <code>intelligence/mod.rs</code> APIs only.</p></li>
<li>
<p>No module under <code>intelligence/*</code> may import from <code>comman=
ds/*</code>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why these rules improve design:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Improves <strong>modularity</strong> (clear dependency direction)</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>Reduces <strong>change amplification</strong> (storage/tooling changes s=
tay in adapters)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Improves <strong>testability</strong> (use cases are unit-testable with =
port fakes)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Preserves <strong>architectural integrity</strong> over time via enforce=
able boundaries</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-6.EarlyRefactoringsRequiredBeforeFeatureBuild-out">6.=
 Early Refactorings Required Before Feature Build-out</h2>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-R1.IntroduceGitClientabstraction">R1. Introduce <code=
>GitClient</code> abstraction</h3>
<p>What to change:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Create <code>adapters/git/client.rs</code> and move direct git process e=
xecution behind this interface.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why first:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Many planned capabilities depend on git history and snapshots.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Current direct subprocess coupling increases duplication and test fragil=
ity.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design improvement:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>dependency inversion</strong> and <strong>mockability</st=
rong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-R2.Replaceinclude!compositioninDevQLandstrategyhotspo=
ts">R2. Replace <code>include!</code> composition in DevQL and strategy hot=
spots</h3>
<p>What to change:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Replace include-based assembly with explicit modules in existing DevQL a=
nd manual commit support areas.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why first:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Planned intelligence migration will otherwise stack complexity on alread=
y opaque boundaries.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design improvement:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>navigability</strong>, <strong>cohesion</strong>, and <st=
rong>explicit module contracts</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-R3.Extractqueryorchestrationbehindintelligence/queryf=
acade">R3. Extract query orchestration behind <code>intelligence/query</cod=
e> facade</h3>
<p>What to change:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Keep existing CLI command shape, but route query execution through <code=
>intelligence/query</code> APIs.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why first:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Avoids feature logic remaining trapped in <code>commands/*</code>.</p></=
li>
</ol>
<p>Design improvement:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>separation of concerns</strong> (delivery adapters vs dom=
ain logic).</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-R4.Addarchitectureguardtestsfordependencyrules">R4. A=
dd architecture guard tests for dependency rules</h3>
<p>What to change:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Add tests that fail on forbidden imports across the above dependency rul=
es.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why first:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Prevents regressions while multiple engineers add modules in parallel.</=
p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design improvement:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>governance</strong> and <strong>architectural drift preve=
ntion</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-7.ImplementationPlan(Explicit,Step-by-Step)">7. Imple=
mentation Plan (Explicit, Step-by-Step)</h2>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step0.Foundation+Contracts">Step 0. Foundation + Cont=
racts</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Create <code>intelligence/contracts/*</code>, <code>intelligence/mod.rs<=
/code>, <code>composition_root.rs</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Define snapshot, artefact, graph, history, tests, clone, provenance cont=
racts.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Establishes shared domain language and stable interfaces.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Improves <strong>ubiquitous language</strong>, <strong>encapsulation</st=
rong>, and <strong>consistency</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Contracts compile and are used by at least one thin query path.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step1.QueryFacadeMigration(NoNewCapabilityYet)">Step =
1. Query Facade Migration (No New Capability Yet)</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Existing DevQL command delegates to <code>intelligence/query/devql/plann=
er.rs</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Preserve existing behavior for current stages.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>De-risks future additions by moving query orchestration into the new bou=
ndary first.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>modularization</strong> and <strong>replaceability</stron=
g>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Existing DevQL tests still pass with new query facade.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step2.IngestionBackbone(Bootstrap+Incremental+Workspa=
ce)">Step 2. Ingestion Backbone (Bootstrap + Incremental + Workspace)</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Implement <code>bootstrap_backfill</code>, <code>incremental_git</code>,=
 <code>workspace_overlay</code> and <code>snapshot_resolver</code>.</p></li=
>
<li>
<p>Add snapshot precedence behavior: workspace -&gt; ref/branch -&gt; expli=
cit commit.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>All downstream capabilities depend on temporal correctness and freshness=
.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>temporal consistency</strong> and <strong>source-of-truth=
 clarity</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Deterministic snapshot selection tests and ingest idempotency checks pas=
s.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step3.Capability#1:BlastRadius">Step 3. Capability #1=
: Blast Radius</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Implement static extractors and <code>graph_builder</code> for initial l=
anguages.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Implement <code>application/capabilities/blast_radius.rs</code> and DevQ=
L stage adapter.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Highest risk-reduction capability for autonomous edits.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Strong <strong>impact analysis correctness</strong> and <strong>dependen=
cy graph utility</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>End-to-end blast radius query returns direct + transitive impact sets.</=
p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step4.Capability#2:HistoricalIntent">Step 4. Capabili=
ty #2: Historical Intent</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Implement <code>provenance/intent_linker.rs</code>, <code>timeline_build=
er.rs</code>, and external refs adapters.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Implement historical intent use case and stage adapter.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Prevents repeated regressions from hidden rationale loss.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>traceability</strong> and <strong>decision provenance</st=
rong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Query returns timeline with linked evidence (commits/checkpoints/docs).<=
/p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step5.Capability#3:TestHarness">Step 5. Capability #3=
: Test Harness</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Implement test inventory + coverage mapping + recommendation logic.</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p>Expose via DevQL stage and API.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Moves agent changes from =E2=80=9Cbest effort=E2=80=9D to evidence-backe=
d verification paths.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>verification completeness</strong> and <strong>quality ga=
tes</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Query returns test candidates, coverage overlap, and untested paths.</p>=
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step6.Capability#4:SemanticClones">Step 6. Capability=
 #4: Semantic Clones</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Implement embedding pipeline, vector index adapter, similarity search us=
e case.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Improves consistency and reuse across large codebases.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>knowledge reuse</strong> and <strong>pattern alignment</s=
trong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Clone query returns ranked similar artefacts with explanation metadata.<=
/p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-Step7.Capability#5:RuntimeProvenanceJoins">Step 7. Ca=
pability #5: Runtime Provenance Joins</h2>
<p>Deliverables:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Implement telemetry bridge and curated joins into provenance model.</p><=
/li>
</ol>
<p>Why this step:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Connects runtime symptoms to code + historical context for safer fixes.<=
/p></li>
</ol>
<p>Design gain:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Better <strong>operational observability</strong> and <strong>root-cause=
 context</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Exit criteria:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Query can explain runtime signal relationships to recent code/intent cha=
nges.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-8.IntegrationPointswithExistingModules">8. Integratio=
n Points with Existing Modules</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><code>commands/devql.rs</code> becomes a thin adapter to <code>intellige=
nce/query</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hook prefetch path integrates with <code>intelligence/application/servic=
es/snapshot_resolver.rs</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Dashboard endpoints consume intelligence use-cases for richer data views=
.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-9.QualityStrategy">9. Quality Strategy</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Unit tests per use case with fake adapters.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Contract tests for adapters (relational/events/vector/git).</p></li>
<li>
<p>Architecture guard tests for dependency rules.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ingestion idempotency and replay tests.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ranking regression benchmarks for planner/ranker.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-10.RisksandMitigations">10. Risks and Mitigations</h2=
>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Risk</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Mitigation</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Migration stalls due broad scope</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Capability-by-capability rollout with behavior-preserving wrappers</p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Query latency regressions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Separate read path planner from write path ingestion and add perf budget=
s</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Schema churn</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Version contracts + explicit migration scripts</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Architectural drift</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Guard tests on forbidden imports/dependency direction</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Over-coupling to one DB setup</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Keep adapter ports for relational/events/vector separation</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"High-LevelDesign/Implementationplanfor:LayeredMVPImplementationfo=
rCodebaseIntelligence-11.DefinitionofSuccess">11. Definition of Success</h2=
>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>New capabilities are added without increasing coupling to <code>commands=
/*</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>At least first three MVP capabilities are available via the query plane.=
</p></li>
<li>
<p>Workspace snapshot precedence works deterministically and is test-covere=
d.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Architecture guard tests prevent dependency-rule violations.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Developers can add a new capability by touching one use case + one stage=
 + adapters, without cross-cutting rewrites.</p></li>
</ol>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
